# nvim
afiy neovim

add
```
mkdir -p ~/.config/nvim/
cat <<EOF > ~/.config/nvim/init.vim
set runtimepath^=~/.vim runtimepath+=~/.vim/afterccc
let &packpath=&runtimepath
source ~/.vimrc
EOF
```

to ~/.config/nvim/init.vim

